This directory contains MATLAB and compiled software for reading data from
various EEG, MEG, fMRI and NIRS devices. The real time data is obtained in
small blocks and copied to a FieldTrip buffer, where MATLAB or another program
can access it.

Most of the source code in this directory is 
Copyright (C) 2009-2015, Donders Institute for Brain, Behaviour and Cognition
Copyright (C) 2007-2009, F.C.  Donders Centre for Cognitive Neuroimaging

Since the software in this directory relies on proprietary interfaces and
hardware drivers, which are often not released under an open source license,
the software in this directory in general is also not covered by an open source
license. Restrictions may apply. Please look in the subdirectories and the
separate files for the specific details.

